TITLE=XVA2IMG
CATEGORY=20:Tools
DESC=Extract IMG disk images from XVA files
ORDER=20
==
<h1>XVA2IMG</h1>
<p>Project repo: <a href='https://github.com/nathan242/xva2img'>LINK</a></p>

<h4>Introduction</h4>
<p>Extracts disk images from XenServer XVA files.</p>
<div class='code'>
<pre>
Convert XVA file to IMG.
USAGE: 
xva2img.py [XVA FILE]
</pre>
</div>

<p>Disk images are extracted into the current directory.</p>
<p>There is an alternative version called "xva2img-extract.py" that will extract the full file structure from the XVA file to a folder before rebuilding the image files. This allows you to examine the XVA contents and perform other tasks after image extraction.</p>

